FAST - CONVENIENT

National ID card (notarized photocopy)
Household registration book (notarized photocopy)
Personal statement (notarized photocopy)
Health check document

Regularly being objectively reviewed by customers

All of our collaborators have the rights to accept tasks on holidays.
